   :safety-property-family
   "**Safety-property family for self-documentation action classes** (`:mission-doc-sync`, `:aif-edn-revision-entry`, `:contract-status-section-update`):

  Autopen-eligibility requires (a) `:match-type :clean` AND (b) structural admissibility against the target's current state.  Class-specific admissibility predicates:

  - `:mission-doc-sync` (L3, claude-2 2026-05-20): target file exists, is git-tracked, has no uncommitted changes at proposal-time (the I7 safety property per M-vsatarcs-writer §3 DERIVE).
