**What landed** (`scripts/generate_vsatarcs_md.bb`):
- New `compute-stub-substrate-index!` precomputes once per regen: `{:inbound-citations {stem #{citing-stem ...}} :issue-queue-by-stem {stem [<entries>]}}`.  Word-boundary regex match across all stories' prose for inbound-citation edges; `:issue-queue` filter over `:pointers` strings.
